<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Portfolio Setup</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: var(--bg-light);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .setup-container {
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 30px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    
    .setup-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .setup-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    
    .setup-steps {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .setup-step {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }
    
    .setup-step:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .setup-step h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-right: 10px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .setup-actions {
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="setup-container">
    <div class="setup-header">
      <h1>Portfolio Setup</h1>
      <p>Follow these steps to set up your portfolio website</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="setup-steps">
      <div class="setup-step">
        <h2><span class="step-number">1</span> Create Admin Account</h2>
        <p>First, you need to create an admin account to manage your portfolio.</p>
        <a href="/auth/setup-admin" class="btn btn-primary">Create Admin Account</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="setup-step">
        <h2><span class="step-number">2</span> Update Your Profile</h2>
        <p>After creating your admin account, update your profile information, including your personal details, education, experience, and skills.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="setup-step">
        <h2><span class="step-number">3</span> Add Your Projects</h2>
        <p>Add your projects to showcase your work. Include project details, images, and links to demos or repositories.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="setup-step">
        <h2><span class="step-number">4</span> Customize Your Portfolio</h2>
        <p>Customize the appearance of your portfolio by updating the CSS styles in the public/css/style.css file.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="setup-actions">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
